Submissions after Friday October 1st and those that are not accepted by October 22nd will still be able to be in Bioconductor but will be included in the development branch until the 3.15 release next Spring.



Please see the release schedule for other important deadlines https://bioconductor.org/developers/release-schedule/

Thank you on behalf of the Core Team




